data.description: Walk to Miracle Mile or enjoy sunset views over Biltmore Way and the Coral Gables Golf Course from your balcony which opens into an enormous living area, dining room and updated kitchen. Only 7 units on each floor and this 1400' corner unit only shares one wall. Each bedroom is open and bright, with large closets and extra storage in every room. Gables Plaza has 24 hour security and concierge, on site management, sparkling pool, Jacuzzi, and 1 deeded garage parking spot. Plenty of street parking available for guests.
